content.rendered:
Welcome to Seanmag 888 Registration & Login.

For Charities not for profits please contact sales@saenmag888.com

(We have a verification process setup for charities and not for profits so they can get approval for discounts. After registration, we will send through further information for verification via email. Please review the tabs below for  information details required.)

Registered Non-Profit Organization

Whether you are ordering a standard or custom amount, you will have to submit a Custom Quote form to obtain a 10% non-profit organization discount towards your regular-priced order. An Estimator will verify your request and provide further instructions for ordering. 

Button Text

OUR GUARANTEE

At Seanmag 888 we understand that everyone wants to get the best deal/savings. You'll find that our price is generally more competitive than any other suppliers in the market. However, we will not compromise our standard of quality as a condition.

Button Text

Charity verification | Non-profit

We are happy to provide a discount to registered non-profit organisations and registered charities. In both cases, we require the following information to determine your eligibility. Registered name of non-profit organisation or charity Registered non-profit organization or charity business number The following details will need to be supplied; For customers in Australia: ABN or ACN For customers in Canada: nine-digit BN/Registration number For customers in U.S: EIN number For customers in China: AIC For customers in Africa For customers in UK: CRN

REGISTERED CHARITIES

Registered charities who can supply a tax receipt are eligible for a 5% discount towards a regular priced order with the already attached discount.  All orders, standard or custom, are to be paid in full via our Place Order page or Custom Quote, and the discount is going to be made in the form of a donation afterward.  For custom orders, please include your registered charity number in the additional comments section of your request, so our business team can take care of your donation request. Please note, the donation request needs to be made before the order is dispatched for shipping or pickup.
